pageContext.claim: “I'm looking at that tape [of Joe Biden recounting how he pressured Ukraine to oust a prosecutor who had been criticized as too corrupt] -- that can't be. And the press, the media, the fake-news media -- and it is fake. It's terrible, actually. But they don't want to put it on. … I never saw anything like this. And you can't find that clip today.”
pageContext.analysis: News organizations prominently reported Biden's demand and the video of his remarks that Trump is referring to. We devoted an entire fact check to the timing and substance of the remarks from the video Trump is talking about.
